&lt;p&gt;The complete code is hosted in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/hantsy/spring4-sandbox/tree/master/groovy-dsl&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;my GitHub account&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

